      ** Define multibranch indicator field
     D RUNDAT          DS
     D  Rundate                8     10P 0
     D  MBIN                  13     13
                                                                                            AR806147
      ** Data structure for date in, to change format.                                      AR806147
     D                 DS                                                                   AR806147
     D  DateIn2                1      8  0                                                  AR806147
     D  @@YY                   1      4  0                                                  AR806147
     D  @@MM                   5      6  0                                                  AR806147
     D  @@DD                   7      8  0                                                  AR806147

